<anchor xml:id="_classgui_1_1inputbox_1_1InputBox_1a2e4482c1a676aee7def02d4020dd4b36"/><section>
    <title>scroll_text()</title>
<indexterm><primary>scroll_text</primary><secondary>gui.inputbox.InputBox</secondary></indexterm>
<indexterm><primary>gui.inputbox.InputBox</primary><secondary>scroll_text</secondary></indexterm>
<para><computeroutput>gui.inputbox.InputBox.scroll_text ( self)</computeroutput></para>
<para><literallayout><computeroutput>Internal method for calculating how and when to scroll text when going beyond the input box.
I am aware of how awful it is. Why? because O(n).
